  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>Prove that a displayed category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> is a cartesian fibration over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E^{\tilde {\mathsf {o}}}]]></fr:tex> is a cocartesian fibration over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B^{\mathsf {op}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
